author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 360
acceptance_criteria: "docs/ gains a composability/scripting reference: exit-code table (success/not-found/validation/conflict/lock classes), the rule that data goes to stdout and diagnostics to stderr, JSON field-name stability policy, and worked grep/jq/xargs recipes; a gate-style spec asserts the exit codes and stream discipline for representative commands so regressions fail CI; README links the reference"
